WEBVTT

00:00:00.919 --> 00:00:03.750
Good morning, family. Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:05.230
Day

00:00:05.240 --> 00:00:09.310
59. I hope you all enjoyed the

00:00:09.320 --> 00:00:12.470
Christmas lights yesterday. We sure did; it

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:13.990
was awesome. Walking around,

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.349
Megan seemed to have a real good time.

00:00:16.359 --> 00:00:18.109
She liked to look at the ducks

00:00:18.119 --> 00:00:20.990
more than anything; she

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:22.870
wanted those ducks to eat that popcorn

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:25.349
so bad. We stood there for a while off-camera

00:00:25.349 --> 00:00:25.359
and tried

00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:29.070
to get

00:00:29.080 --> 00:00:30.509
those ducks to come over, but those

00:00:30.519 --> 00:00:33.790
ducks were not having it.

00:00:33.800 --> 00:00:35.590
God is so good; I love all His little

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:38.270
creatures He's made. Like Bob

00:00:38.270 --> 00:00:38.280
Ross—he

00:00:38.280 --> 00:00:40.510
takes

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:42.630
Peanut the pocket squirrel and

00:00:42.640 --> 00:00:44.950
has those little pigeons and

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:46.630
all that stuff he used to carry

00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:47.790
around with him when he was painting

00:00:47.800 --> 00:00:49.029
those

00:00:49.039 --> 00:00:51.950
pictures. We loved all that; we still

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:54.510
watch those reruns. My son

00:00:54.520 --> 00:00:57.310
used to pretend he was Bob Ross and

00:00:57.320 --> 00:01:00.430
paint pictures for me.

00:01:00.440 --> 00:01:02.470
God is good, and

00:01:02.480 --> 00:01:04.350
I just love His nature.

00:01:04.360 --> 00:01:06.590
Thank you for joining

00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:08.789
us yesterday; we appreciate it, Diana. We

00:01:08.799 --> 00:01:10.670
think it's fun and thought about doing

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:12.590
more vlogs like that so you

00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:14.910
all can see our day and go

00:01:14.920 --> 00:01:17.030
around with us,

00:01:17.040 --> 00:01:19.630
but it's

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:22.310
something different every once in a

00:01:22.320 --> 00:01:24.069
while. We made fun of it

00:01:24.069 --> 00:01:24.079
regarding

00:01:24.079 --> 00:01:26.550
the Bubba and

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:28.550
the drones flying over. They

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:31.670
don't just fly over Oklahoma;

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:34.510
they're looking for

00:01:34.520 --> 00:01:37.190
something. Those are military; they have

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:38.870
to

00:01:38.880 --> 00:01:43.990
be. We have one of the most

00:01:43.990 --> 00:01:44.000
top-secret

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:47.510
governments in the world, and

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:49.749
you're telling me we have hundreds of

00:01:49.759 --> 00:01:52.270
these drones flying around and

00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:53.389
they're like, 'Well, we don't know what

00:01:53.399 --> 00:01:56.709
they are'? Baloney,

00:01:56.719 --> 00:01:59.469
y'all! They do know what they are. I

00:01:59.479 --> 00:02:01.749
told you this is something they're

00:02:01.759 --> 00:02:04.749
going to start using all the time; this

00:02:04.759 --> 00:02:08.029
is going to be a

00:02:08.039 --> 00:02:12.190
way of life for what's coming.

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:13.670
They're going to start using these

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:15.030
drones

00:02:15.040 --> 00:02:17.509
everywhere. We don't even have the

00:02:17.519 --> 00:02:19.710
next administration in, and he's talking

00:02:19.720 --> 00:02:21.430
about shooting them out of the sky

00:02:21.430 --> 00:02:21.440
because

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:23.949
he's not being briefed on the security

00:02:23.959 --> 00:02:26.150
all the way, it sounds like. For

00:02:26.160 --> 00:02:28.350
people to sit there and say, 'Well, I got a

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:30.190
prophetic word,'and some people

00:02:30.200 --> 00:02:31.869
saying it's

00:02:31.869 --> 00:02:31.879
aliens—maybe

00:02:31.879 --> 00:02:34.869
I'm wrong, maybe it is, but I

00:02:34.879 --> 00:02:41.149
feel in my heart it's a desensitizing of

00:02:41.159 --> 00:02:43.630
things. We are

00:02:43.640 --> 00:02:47.589
seeing the Beast

00:02:47.599 --> 00:02:50.390
system unfolding right in front of our

00:02:50.390 --> 00:02:50.400
faces:

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:53.869
how they're going to use

00:02:53.879 --> 00:02:57.309
technology to track you.

00:02:58.440 --> 00:03:00.949
They're just playing a poker match and bringing out their

00:03:02.670 --> 00:03:02.680
cards,

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:06.149
showing you they have a

00:03:06.159 --> 00:03:06.990
full

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.990
house. They're

00:03:09.990 --> 00:03:10.000
one-up

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:12.550
on you, and you're still

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:15.070
stuck on the technology from five or ten years

00:03:15.080 --> 00:03:17.949
ago. They're

00:03:17.949 --> 00:03:17.959
light-years

00:03:17.959 --> 00:03:20.390
ahead of you. They've got technology that

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:22.710
you don't have any clue about. I've

00:03:22.720 --> 00:03:24.750
told you about that pulse thing that

00:03:24.760 --> 00:03:26.430
they're going to bring out

00:03:26.430 --> 00:03:26.440
for

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:28.910
crowd control. If they can't

00:03:28.920 --> 00:03:31.949
use firearms on people, they're

00:03:31.949 --> 00:03:31.959
just

00:03:31.959 --> 00:03:33.910
going to knock people out in the

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:35.350
crowd, and it will look like they

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:36.670
just passed out

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:39.589
everywhere instead of using gas

00:03:39.589 --> 00:03:39.599
or

00:03:39.599 --> 00:03:42.750
smoke from riots.

00:03:42.760 --> 00:03:44.429
Whenever people are looting

00:03:44.439 --> 00:03:45.710
and acting

00:03:45.720 --> 00:03:48.429
nuts, they use gas and

00:03:48.439 --> 00:03:50.070
pepper spray

00:03:50.070 --> 00:03:50.080
to

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:53.429
make the

00:03:53.439 --> 00:03:56.030
crowds

00:03:56.040 --> 00:03:58.149
obey. They'll just use this new

00:03:58.159 --> 00:04:00.110
technology, and people

00:04:00.110 --> 00:04:00.120
will

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:01.750
fall like

00:04:01.760 --> 00:04:05.670
flies. I'm telling you, it's coming.

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:08.670
When I went to tribulation with the Lord,

00:04:08.680 --> 00:04:11.350
all the things He showed me

00:04:11.360 --> 00:04:13.030
we're starting to see more

00:04:13.040 --> 00:04:15.229
and more on the

00:04:15.239 --> 00:04:18.310
news. You all don't realize how

00:04:18.320 --> 00:04:20.830
close we are to His coming. I told you we

00:04:20.840 --> 00:04:22.430
would start to see more

00:04:22.440 --> 00:04:26.150
signs in the heavens, and the

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:28.670
drones are just part of

00:04:28.670 --> 00:04:28.680
the

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:30.629
surveillance in society. They're going

00:04:30.639 --> 00:04:33.110
to start doing this in China, Europe,

00:04:33.110 --> 00:04:33.120
and

00:04:33.120 --> 00:04:35.189
the Middle East. We're going to start

00:04:35.199 --> 00:04:38.950
seeing this everywhere, and people will

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:41.990
become more used to it instead of saying,

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:44.070
'Is it delivering a package?'No, it's

00:04:44.080 --> 00:04:46.749
just a police drone circling

00:04:46.759 --> 00:04:49.550
and surveilling the area to make sure

00:04:49.560 --> 00:04:54.189
people are safe. Interesting.

00:04:54.199 --> 00:04:56.990
So, nothing to be alarmed about, folks.

00:04:57.000 --> 00:04:59.830
Jesus is coming; this is just part of the

00:04:59.840 --> 00:05:02.150
Beast system coming to pass. It's

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:05.350
exciting because I know what comes

00:05:05.360 --> 00:05:08.790
next: a massive

00:05:08.800 --> 00:05:11.870
revival that's about to take place

00:05:11.870 --> 00:05:11.880
and

00:05:11.880 --> 00:05:14.950
an outpouring of finances.

00:05:14.960 --> 00:05:17.670
The Lord showed

00:05:17.680 --> 00:05:20.790
me even this

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:23.150
yesterday. When I was driving

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:24.990
home from the lights, the Lord said,

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:26.550
'Brandon, I want you to drive around for a

00:05:26.550 --> 00:05:26.560
bit;

00:05:26.560 --> 00:05:28.230
I have some things I have to talk

00:05:28.240 --> 00:05:32.189
to you about.'I told Diana, 'We

00:05:32.199 --> 00:05:34.150
can't go home yet; the Lord wants

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:36.550
to talk.'So I just started driving

00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:38.110
and praying in the spirit.

00:05:38.120 --> 00:05:40.909
Deep groanings came in the

00:05:40.919 --> 00:05:43.070
spirit; I started interceding, and

00:05:43.080 --> 00:05:45.950
it was like a waterfall coming up

00:05:45.960 --> 00:05:47.230
out of

00:05:47.240 --> 00:05:49.430
me. Diana and the kids were just

00:05:49.440 --> 00:05:52.270
praying and

00:05:52.280 --> 00:05:55.270
interceding for what the Lord wanted

00:05:55.280 --> 00:05:58.909
to talk about. It was about

00:05:58.919 --> 00:06:00.950
what's coming with the

00:06:00.960 --> 00:06:03.150
finances; He was giving me

00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:05.629
impartation

00:06:05.639 --> 00:06:08.029
about what's coming.

00:06:08.039 --> 00:06:11.189
He told me we're not

00:06:11.199 --> 00:06:14.870
believing big enough

00:06:14.870 --> 00:06:14.880
and

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:19.029
to enlarge our capacity in our minds to

00:06:19.039 --> 00:06:22.230
think bigger by reading His word, to

00:06:22.240 --> 00:06:23.830
believe Him for

00:06:23.840 --> 00:06:26.950
exceedingly abundantly above all that

00:06:26.960 --> 00:06:30.589
you dare ask or think. He said, 'I

00:06:30.599 --> 00:06:33.029
want you to think about that: how much

00:06:33.039 --> 00:06:34.309
can you think

00:06:34.319 --> 00:06:38.990
for over and above all that you

00:06:38.990 --> 00:06:39.000
think?'I

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:42.110
can think some big things, folks. Can you

00:06:42.120 --> 00:06:44.390
believe God for big?

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:47.150
You have all kinds of hopes,

00:06:47.160 --> 00:06:49.950
desires, and dreams, don't you?

00:06:49.960 --> 00:06:52.790
As a man thinks

00:06:52.800 --> 00:06:55.469
in his heart, so is he. The Lord was

00:06:55.479 --> 00:06:57.950
showing me, 'Brandon, I'm going to

00:06:57.960 --> 00:07:01.749
do even

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:03.550
exceedingly

00:07:03.560 --> 00:07:08.749
abundantly above all that you dare ask

00:07:08.759 --> 00:07:12.950
me for or

00:07:12.950 --> 00:07:12.960
think.'He

00:07:12.960 --> 00:07:15.189
was talking about the thinking part

00:07:15.199 --> 00:07:17.029
because people can think big, but He said,

00:07:17.039 --> 00:07:18.390
'Brandon, you've got to even think bigger

00:07:18.400 --> 00:07:19.909
than what you

00:07:19.919 --> 00:07:22.270
think because of what I'm about to do in

00:07:22.280 --> 00:07:25.469
this earth.'Folks, He's about to show up

00:07:25.479 --> 00:07:28.430
and show off in your life.

00:07:31.560 --> 00:07:35.110
I hear the sound of an

00:07:35.120 --> 00:07:37.029
abundance of

00:07:37.039 --> 00:07:40.110
rain, and the camels are

00:07:40.120 --> 00:07:43.629
coming, loaded down with

00:07:43.639 --> 00:07:47.430
everything you've been believing God for,

00:07:47.440 --> 00:07:49.830
everything you've stretched your hand

00:07:49.840 --> 00:07:52.469
out and sowed to believe sacrificially.

00:07:56.840 --> 00:07:59.270
Do you ever take a calculator

00:07:59.270 --> 00:07:59.280
to

00:07:59.280 --> 00:08:02.309
what you've sowed over the course? Maybe

00:08:02.319 --> 00:08:05.270
you have a record of it.

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:06.589
Even the seeds that you may have

00:08:06.599 --> 00:08:08.909
forgotten about, ask the Holy Spirit

00:08:08.909 --> 00:08:08.919
to

00:08:08.919 --> 00:08:11.510
help you remember

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:14.629
all the things that you have sowed in the

00:08:14.639 --> 00:08:18.430
past. He said some thirty, some sixty, and some

00:08:18.440 --> 00:08:19.830
hundredfold.

00:08:19.840 --> 00:08:22.869
Take a calculator and do the math

00:08:22.879 --> 00:08:25.629
on what is being laid up

00:08:25.639 --> 00:08:30.469
for you. Seedtime and

00:08:30.479 --> 00:08:35.990
harvest: seed sowing is a law, but harvest

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:39.350
is a law just as much.

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:43.389
The Lord told me that

00:08:43.399 --> 00:08:46.350
reaping

00:08:46.360 --> 00:08:48.949
is just as much a law as

00:08:48.949 --> 00:08:48.959
sowing.

00:08:48.959 --> 00:08:52.750
We have got to learn that

00:08:52.760 --> 00:08:55.990
it's time for us to reap. He said you

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:58.870
will reap if you faint not.

00:08:58.880 --> 00:09:00.710
But a lot of you give up

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:03.190
on your old seed. You

00:09:03.200 --> 00:09:05.750
go, 'Well, it didn't come to pass

00:09:05.760 --> 00:09:07.550
over the last five years, so I guess

00:09:07.560 --> 00:09:09.590
that seed's

00:09:09.600 --> 00:09:11.150
dead.'I

00:09:11.160 --> 00:09:14.389
believe the Lord said the seeds you

00:09:14.399 --> 00:09:17.550
have sowed in the past will come to

00:09:17.560 --> 00:09:20.829
harvest at last. In

00:09:20.839 --> 00:09:23.710
2025, you're going to see a multiplication

00:09:23.710 --> 00:09:23.720
of

00:09:23.720 --> 00:09:27.630
your harvest time. The

00:09:27.630 --> 00:09:27.640
sowers

00:09:27.640 --> 00:09:29.910
and the reapers are going to

00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:34.190
start going hand in hand, and as you

00:09:34.190 --> 00:09:34.200
sow,

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:37.269
you're going to start to reap

00:09:37.279 --> 00:09:39.509
instantaneously. What you say out of your

00:09:39.519 --> 00:09:41.150
mouth and what you believe in your heart

00:09:41.160 --> 00:09:43.509
is going to start to come to pass. I

00:09:43.519 --> 00:09:46.829
believe with all my heart this is a time

00:09:46.839 --> 00:09:51.750
for you to believe

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:55.710
big: spiritually, physically, emotionally,

00:09:55.710 --> 00:09:55.720
and

00:09:55.720 --> 00:09:58.310
mentally. You may say,

00:09:58.320 --> 00:10:00.829
'I don't need finances; I'm rich.'Well, you

00:10:00.839 --> 00:10:03.389
may need something in your body.

00:10:03.399 --> 00:10:06.389
God is a healer, and He said,

00:10:06.399 --> 00:10:08.430
'Beloved, I wish above all things that you

00:10:08.440 --> 00:10:12.150
prosper and be in health, even as your

00:10:12.160 --> 00:10:15.829
soul prospers.'Prosperity is not just

00:10:15.839 --> 00:10:20.990
about finances; it's about living in

00:10:21.000 --> 00:10:23.550
wholeness mentally, emotionally,

00:10:23.560 --> 00:10:25.710
physically, and financially. Your

00:10:25.710 --> 00:10:25.720
marriage—people

00:10:25.720 --> 00:10:28.069
go, 'I'm

00:10:28.079 --> 00:10:29.829
rich and whole in my body, but my

00:10:29.839 --> 00:10:32.030
marriage is terrible and my kids talk to me

00:10:32.030 --> 00:10:32.040
terribly.'That's

00:10:32.040 --> 00:10:35.030
not whole. He wants

00:10:35.040 --> 00:10:39.750
you to be made whole

00:10:39.760 --> 00:10:42.230
through everything abundantly above all

00:10:42.240 --> 00:10:43.949
that you dare ask or think.

00:10:55.480 --> 00:10:58.069
I want my marriage good,

00:10:58.079 --> 00:11:00.150
my children healthy,

00:11:00.160 --> 00:11:02.230
my health good,

00:11:02.230 --> 00:11:02.240
and

00:11:02.240 --> 00:11:04.750
a

00:11:04.760 --> 00:11:06.230
good job.

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:10.990
Do you see? He wants you to live

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:13.470
an abundant life. The

00:11:13.480 --> 00:11:16.750
Lord told me from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah, which

00:11:16.760 --> 00:11:19.069
was last October, you'll start to

00:11:19.079 --> 00:11:23.030
see first the blade, then the ear, then

00:11:23.040 --> 00:11:25.430
the full manifestation on that

00:11:25.440 --> 00:11:29.550
ear. The Lord told me you would start

00:11:29.560 --> 00:11:32.509
to see the glory in different

00:11:32.519 --> 00:11:36.230
levels: ankle-deep,

00:11:36.230 --> 00:11:36.240
knee-deep, waist-deep,

00:11:36.240 --> 00:11:38.470
and over the top. It's

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:40.069
time to go down to the bottom of that

00:11:40.079 --> 00:11:43.470
pool at His altar. I believe it's a time

00:11:43.480 --> 00:11:47.069
like never before that we are joint

00:11:47.069 --> 00:11:47.079
heirs

00:11:47.079 --> 00:11:51.110
of Jesus Christ and we display

00:11:51.120 --> 00:11:54.389
kingliness. We show it off

00:11:54.389 --> 00:11:54.399
so

00:11:54.399 --> 00:11:57.150
that people see that inside of us.

00:11:57.150 --> 00:11:57.160
Yes,

00:11:57.160 --> 00:11:58.870
all this stuff's going on around us, and

00:11:58.880 --> 00:12:00.829
there's a lot of drama

00:12:00.839 --> 00:12:04.030
on the news

00:12:04.040 --> 00:12:08.110
every day. But my

00:12:08.120 --> 00:12:10.550
goodness, y'all, we're about to see the

00:12:10.560 --> 00:12:13.829
glorious church rise and

00:12:13.839 --> 00:12:16.389
the greatest harvest of souls this

00:12:16.399 --> 00:12:19.269
world has ever known. It's all going

00:12:19.279 --> 00:12:21.670
to come through you, for you were called

00:12:21.680 --> 00:12:24.670
to the kingdom for such a time as this.

00:12:24.680 --> 00:12:27.509
I'm seeing

00:12:27.519 --> 00:12:29.269
people freaking out on the

00:12:29.269 --> 00:12:29.279
news, but

00:12:29.279 --> 00:12:30.790
it's just part of it. They're

00:12:30.800 --> 00:12:32.949
using the drones for surveillance;

00:12:35.199 --> 00:12:37.750
they're looking for something. It's not

00:12:37.760 --> 00:12:39.710
aliens

00:12:39.710 --> 00:12:39.720
or

00:12:39.720 --> 00:12:41.509
spooky stuff;

00:12:41.509 --> 00:12:41.519
it's

00:12:41.519 --> 00:12:43.350
technology you don't even realize they

00:12:43.360 --> 00:12:45.269
have. They're orbs and all this

00:12:45.279 --> 00:12:46.710
other stuff coming in and out of the

00:12:46.720 --> 00:12:51.069
water.

00:12:51.079 --> 00:12:53.150
We're looking at AI

